zeus.concepts
Class FIPA_MTP_Description

java.lang.Object
  zeus.concepts.FIPA_MTP_Description
public class FIPA_MTP_Description
extends java.lang.Object

FIPA_MTP_Description is used to store the result of parsing a mtp-description fragment. The toString method can be used to generate a FIPA format string for sending message transport profiles to agents on other platforms.

Since:
1.2
Author:
Simon Thompson
